  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK520">
<l>nāṭōṟu nāṭuka maṉṉaṉ viṉaiceyvāṉ</l>
<l> kōṭāmai kōṭā tulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a king daily examine the conduct of his servants; if they do not act crookedly, the world will not act crookedly.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
